author: maxb
msg: Merge r16480 from trunk to 1.3.x branch.
Remove compatibility code for old versions of SWIG (SWIG 1.3.24 is now
required).
Approved by: +1: maxb, djames

author: maxb
msg: Merge r16479 from trunk to 1.3.x branch.
Make _global_svn_swig_py_is_local_pool a local variable instead of a global
variable. Use _global_pool_is_application_pool instead of
_global_svn_swig_py_is_local_pool. Rename _global_is_default_pool to
_global_pool_is_default_pool.
Approved by: +1: djames, +0: maxb

author: maxb
msg: Merge r16470 from trunk to 1.3.x branch.
Move proxy_apr.swg from proxy/ to include/, leaving proxy/ to be a
directory solely for build-time generated files.
Approved by: +1: maxb, djames

author: maxb
msg: Merge r16465 from trunk to 1.3.x branch.
Fix erroneous %include of apr.h into SWIG Perl and Ruby bindings, which
was causing many irrelevant APR feature macros to be imported into the core
modules.
Approved by: +1: maxb, djames

author: maxb
